dct_title_s: Ship Channel, leading from Exuma Sound across the New Providence Bank towards the tongue of the ocean
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. At head of title: West Indies, Bahamas. "1509." Includes profile: View of the Cays from A. Historic Maps copy has label on verso: West Indies. Ship Channel. 1569.
